Package com.github.dandelion.datatables.jsp.tag

Class Summary
AbstractColumnTag Superclass of ColumnTag containing: tag attributes declaration (note that all the corresponding setters are in the ColumnTag helper attributes and methods used to initialize the column Note that this tag supports dynamic attributes with only string values.
AbstractTableTag Superclass of TableTag containing: tag attributes declaration (note that all the corresponding setters are in the TableTag helper attributes and methods used to initialize the table
CallbackTag JSP tag used to add a DataTables callback.
CaptionTag JSP tag used to generate a HTML caption tag.
ColumnHeadTag JSP tag used to add a specific content inside a column header.
ColumnTag JSP tag used for creating a table column.
ExportTag JSP tag used to configure an export type in the current table.
ExtraHtmlTag JSP tag used to create a HTML snippet and insert it anywhere around the table thanks to the TableConfig.FEATURE_DOM configuration.
ExtraJsTag JSP tag used to insert an etra Javascript file inside the one generated by Dandelion-DataTables.
PropTag JSP tag used to overload locally a configuration property.
TableTag JSP tag used for creating HTML tables.
